overview.en: UBI.city is a decentralized organizational governance protocol which realizes the vision of UBI. UBI.city solves the problem of sybil attacks and realizes the value of personal tokens by introducing Proof of Performance. UBI.city has designed a system with a decentralized protocol for users to support UBI.city to connect to the DeFi system on ETH1.0.
overview.zh: UBI.city是一个去中心化的组织治理协议，它实现了UBI的愿景。 UBI.city通过引入POP证明解决了sybil攻击的问题并实现了个人代币的价值。 UBI.city设计了一个具有去中心化协议的系统，供用户支持UBI.city连接到ETH1.0上的DeFi生态。
